/**
* <div id="function.mysql-get-proto-info" class="refentry"> <div class="refnamediv">  <h1 class="refname">mysql_get_proto_info</h1>  <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.0.5, PHP 5)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">mysql_get_proto_info</span> — <span class="dc-title">取得 MySQL 协议信息</span></p> </div> <div id="function.mysql-get-proto-info-refsynopsisdiv">  <div class="warning"><strong class="warning">警告</strong>   <p class="para">本扩展自 PHP 5.5.0起已废弃，并在自 PHP 7.0.0 开始被移除。应使用 <a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/book.mysqli.php" class="link">MySQLi</a>或 <a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/ref.pdo-mysql.php" class="link">PDO_MySQL</a> 扩展来替换之。参见 <a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/mysqlinfo.api.choosing.php" class="link">MySQL：选择 API</a> 指南来获取更多信息。用以替代本函数的有：</p>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/mysqli.get-proto-info.php" class="function">mysqli_get_proto_info()</a></span></li>   </ul>  </div> </div> <div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.mysql-get-proto-info-description">  <h3 class="title">说明</h3>  <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">   <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>mysql_get_proto_info</strong></span>(<span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">$link_identifier</span><span class="initializer"> = NULL</span></span>): <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.singleton.php" class="type false" style="color:#EAB766">false</a></span></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">   检索 MySQL 协议。  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.mysql-get-proto-info-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>    <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">link_identifier</span></dt><dd><p class="para">MySQL连接。如不指定连接标识，则使用由 <span class="function">{@link mysql_connect()}</span>最近打开的连接。如果没有找到该连接，会尝试不带参数调用<span class="function">{@link mysql_connect()}</span>来创建。如没有找到连接或无法建立连接，则会生成<strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/errorfunc.constants.php#constant.e-warning">E_WARNING</a></span></strong> 级别的错误。</p></dd>   </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.mysql-get-proto-info-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns the MySQL protocol on success 或者在失败时返回 <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong>.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.mysql-get-proto-info-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-1881">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>mysql_get_proto_info()</strong></span> 示例</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>$link </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">mysql_connect</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'localhost'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'mysql_user'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'mysql_password'</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>if (!</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$link</span><span style="color: #007700">) {<br>    die(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'Could not connect: ' </span><span style="color: #007700">. </span><span style="color: #9876AA">mysql_error</span><span style="color: #007700">());<br>}<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">printf</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"MySQL protocol version: %s\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">mysql_get_proto_info</span><span style="color: #007700">());<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>    <div class="example-contents"><p>以上示例的输出类似于：</p></div>    <div class="example-contents screen" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><div class="examplescode"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;">MySQL protocol version: 10</blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.mysql-get-proto-info-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link mysql_get_client_info()} - 取得 MySQL 客户端信息</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link mysql_get_host_info()} - 取得 MySQL 主机信息</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link mysql_get_server_info()} - 取得 MySQL 服务器信息</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
